      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Error节点是e = T_meas - T_phys，这个误差信号送到LNN对吧？不是送回PINN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "LNN",
        "PINN"
