      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，误差反馈给LNN，让在线学习器去修正。PINN是固定的物理模型，不需要这个误差反馈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "LNN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接Error到LNN。那LNN的输出去哪里？和PINN的输出汇合吗？",
